<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container">
  <h1 class="mt-5">⚡ Pokemon API</h1>

  <p>This is a simple REST API for managing Pokemons, Trainers and Types.</p>

  <h2>📌 Pokemon Endpoints</h2>

  <div class="endpoint">
    <p><code>GET /pokemons</code> — get all pokemons</p>
    <p><code>GET /pokemons/:id</code> — get pokemon by id</p>
    <p><code>POST /pokemons</code> — create new pokemon</p>
    <p><code>PATCH /pokemons/:id</code> — update pokemon</p>
    <p><code>DELETE /pokemons/:id</code> — delete pokemon</p>

    <hr />

    <p><code>GET /pokemons?type=1</code> — get pokemons by type</p>
    <p><code>GET /pokemons?trainerId=2</code> — get pokemons of a trainer</p>
  </div>

  <h2>👤 Trainer Endpoints</h2>

  <div class="endpoint">
    <p><code>GET /trainers</code> — get all trainers</p>
    <p><code>GET /trainers/:id</code> — get trainer by id</p>
    <p><code>POST /trainers</code> — create trainer</p>
    <p><code>PATCH /trainers/:id</code> — update trainer</p>
    <p><code>DELETE /trainers/:id</code> — delete trainer</p>

    <hr />

    <p>
      <code>GET /trainers/:id?type=1</code> — get trainer's pokemons filtered by
      type
    </p>
    <p>
      <code>GET /trainers?pokemonId=2</code> — get trainers who own a pokemon
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2>🏷️ Type Endpoints</h2>

  <div class="endpoint">
    <p><code>GET /types</code> — get all types</p>
    <p><code>GET /types/:id</code> — get type by id</p>
    <p><code>POST /types</code> — create new type</p>
    <p><code>PATCH /types/:id</code> — update type</p>
    <p><code>DELETE /types/:id</code> — delete type</p>
  </div>

  <h2>🔗 Relations (Filtering)</h2>

  <div class="endpoint">
    <p><code>GET /pokemons?type=1</code> — filter pokemons by type</p>
    <p><code>GET /pokemons?trainerId=2</code> — filter pokemons by trainer</p>
    <p>
      <code>GET /trainers/:id?type=1</code> — filter trainer's pokemons by type
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2>🚀 Notes</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>All data is stored in memory (mock data)</li>
    <li>No database is used</li>
    <li>Supports JSON requests only</li>
    <li>Types are shared across all pokemons</li>
  </ul>
</div>

